CREATE VIEW BUSINESS_RULES.COMPONENT_S_PSA
AS

  SELECT 
    bo."BK Component",                                -- Business Key for Hub Component
    bo."Component Name",                              -- PACKAGE_NAME from Satellite Component > PSA > Main
    bo."Component Descritpion",                       -- PACKAGE_DESCRIPTION from Satellite Component > PSA > Main
    bo."Component Layer",                             -- PACKAGE_LAYER from Satellite Component > PSA > Main
    bo."Component Version Description",               -- COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION from Satellite Component > PSA > Main
    bo."Component Version",                           -- COMPONENT_VERSION from Satellite Component > PSA > Main
    bo."Cluster",                                     -- PACKAGE_AUTOSARCLUSTER from Satellite Component > PSA > AUTOSAR Attributes
    bo."Module",                                      -- PACKAGE_SHORTNAME from Satellite Component > PSA > AUTOSAR Attributes
    bo."PS Component - PSA - AUTOSAR Attributes",     -- Entry Present in Satellite Component > PSA > AUTOSAR Attributes
    bo."LTS Component - PSA - AUTOSAR Attributes",    -- Load Time Satellite Component > PSA > AUTOSAR Attributes
    bo."LTS Component - PSA - Main"                   -- Load Time Satellite Component > PSA > Main

  FROM BUSINESSOBJECTS.COMPONENT_S_PSA bo
